# [Cycle 2 — long climbing chase; full sequence available in Unity console; truncated for brevity]
# Engage state held for 32.72 s. Bank oscillated to -0.70 clamp; pitch +0.50 clamp; throttle saturated 1.00 most of cycle.
# Altitude climbed 704 → 781 then descended 781 → 621 chasing diving target. Speed dropped 63.8 → 44.2 m/s (near stall).
# fire=1 observed on 2 ticks at alt=644 and alt=625 (close-fire window briefly achieved during steep dive).
[AI] Engage → Disengage  range=49m  alt=621m  vy=-22.5m/s  dwelled=32.72s
